(Theorem 1 from 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Abraham2008"

\end_inset

).
 Consider 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{G}$
\end_inset

 a weighted graph.
 There exists a tree 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{T}$
\end_inset

 that is a subgraph of 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{G}$
\end_inset

 so that: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
L_{G}\preceq L_{T}\preceq\kappa L_{G}
\]

\end_inset

with 
\begin_inset Formula $\kappa=Cm\log n\log\log n\left(\log\log\log n\right)^{3}$
\end_inset

 for some constant 
\begin_inset Formula $C>0$
\end_inset

.
