 Its PLD can be computed up to a precision of 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon$
\end_inset

 and with high probability in time 
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{O}\left(mn\left(\epsilon^{-1}+\frac{1}{n\epsilon^{2}}\right)\left(\log m\right)^{3}\left(\log n\right)^{2}\log\epsilon^{-1}\right)$
\end_inset

.
